Description Set the current active authentication context.
Command codefresh auth use-context &lt;name&gt;
Arguments    Option Alias Default Description     name   a context-name that exists in cfconfig file    Options    Option Alias Default Description     - -help   Print help information    Examples Set active authentication context to NAME codefresh auth use-context NAME

